vely. Overall, together with studies in other land and aquatic animals, our work supports that seasonal gene expression variations may be a general evolutionary response to environmental changes in wild animals.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Chen, Wenli", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mao, Xiuguang", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/0c86c45da98a38a2f34e4ee0af94e9fe", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/a8cc5013e0088ad7c588a0d0a3e98fe0a00702619232e7935161dcf62692e170", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/Y8HQLN4D", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/Y8HQLN4D", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/46108d2e5ae334daf76f87a2e14e1ce7!/b237856-240317", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "5", "pages": "e8923", "title": "Ecology and Evolution", "volume": "12"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/0c86c45da98a38a2f34e4ee0af94e9fe"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:Y8HQLN4D"}, {"identifier": "10.1002/ece3.8923"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13468540"}}]}}, "title